<p>‚ÄìYes, sure but I wondered about a few things like where you‚Äôve got this <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Array%20data%20structure" title="Wikipedia: Array data structure">array</a> of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Floating%20point" title="Wikipedia: Floating point">reals</a> here, what‚Äôs that?</p>
