<p>‚ÄìLeo, it‚Äôs symbolic. Today‚Äôs <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armistice%20Day" title="Wikipedia: Armistice Day">Armistice Day</a>, you know?</p>
<p>‚ÄìShit on that, it‚Äôs to embarrass us. All for Chase. Man keeps calling me up about twenty kilos of plutonium gone missing<a href="#fn45" class="footnoteRef" id="fnref45"><sup>45</sup></a>, I keep telling him we don‚Äôt stockpile plutonium here.</p>
