<p>‚ÄìWell, Bernd, Chase doesn‚Äôt have the clearance to know that, and picking up the phone midring, ‚ÄìYes? Damn it Dennis just, look, take him to the downstairs conference room think you can do that? ‚Ä¶no will you forget the fucking slides, thumbing the phone‚Äôs button, ‚Äì Where‚Äôs Szabo? You all go down, I‚Äôm right behind you.</p>
<p>‚ÄìSenator, glad you could make it. This all? Expected to see more of your colleagues‚Ä¶</p>
<p>‚ÄìDoctor Highet. These two gentlemen are from the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/General%20Accounting%20Office" title="Wikipedia: General Accounting Office">General Accounting Office</a>. You‚Äôll be seeing more of them. [pg67]</p>
<p>‚ÄìWhy don‚Äôt you all take a seat and we‚Äôll begin.</p>
<p>‚ÄìI have just one question, Doctor Highet. Is the Superbright going to work?</p>
<p>‚ÄìI believe our presentation will address any</p>
<p>‚ÄìI don‚Äôt want a presentation, I want a yes or no. At the present moment, judging from everything you have to date, is it a viable system, within the budget and timeframe we have?</p>
<p>‚ÄìBeyond question. In fact we have new results that show</p>
