<p>‚ÄìI‚Äôm glad Bernd brought this up. It‚Äôs stressful but it‚Äôs nothing new. The Radiance program has some unresolved issues, we know this. We also know that we can resolve them. But in the meantime our [pg90] critics are getting vocal. Is there anyone here who can‚Äôt take the heat?</p>
