<p>From the closet he took a garment bag and checked its contents: his impression-management suit, a tie, two clean shirts, socks, a pair of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rockport%20%28company%29" title="Wikipedia: Rockport (company)">Rockports</a>, a personal kit. Again he lifted the phone. His left eyelid began to twitch. Phon in hand he pressed a finger against it. With the other hand he punched 276-7384. Behind him his fax machine purred.</p>
