<p>‚ÄìMorning, Philip, said Szabo, suddenly at Quine‚Äôs side as they entered the conference room. ‚ÄìI see Good Friday is April Fool‚Äôs Day this year. It‚Äôs like the anarchists‚Äô convention out there. How many have they got, fifteen, twenty? What‚Äôs that, coffee? Not your usual</p>
