<p>‚ÄìBut to enable them to what? Walk your path, from science to weapons? [pg331] She took his hand. ‚ÄìYou remember last summer? Right here. We kissed for the first time. Nothing seemed impossible then.</p>
<p>‚ÄìNo.</p>
<p>‚ÄìAnd now we‚Äôre so much closer!</p>
<p>‚ÄìCloser‚Ä¶?</p>
