<p>‚ÄìI just, sometimes I just want to give up. But if you think it‚Äôs all so compromised, what about me? Why are you with me?</p>
<p>‚ÄìBecause I trust you, Philip. That you want to do the right thing. And it‚Äôs so hard for you. Do you trust me?</p>
<p>‚ÄìTrust? as something fled across his face looking for a place to hide, and was trapped there. ‚ÄìYes I, of course I, I mean‚Ä¶</p>
