<p>‚ÄìWhat makes you think</p>
<p>‚Äì‚ÄúStates parties to the treaty undertake not to place in orbit [pg337] around the Earth any objects carrying nuclear weapons.‚Äù Outer Space Treaty, nineteen sixty seven. North Korea never signed.<a href="#fn153" class="footnoteRef" id="fnref153"><sup>153</sup></a></p>
