<p>‚ÄìMe? I just provide information. For example, a nuke dropped from an orbiting platform takes under five minutes to hit the ground. Or, you can set it off in low orbit and the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nuclear%20electromagnetic%20pulse" title="Wikipedia: Nuclear electromagnetic pulse">EM pulse</a> will take out military C3, computers, telephones, broadcasting, banking, toasters, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Game%20Boy" title="Wikipedia: Game Boy">gameboys</a>, you name it.</p>
