<p>‚ÄìI know how demanding you are. It might not meet your high standards. Personally, I wouldn‚Äôt have promised ignition.<a href="#fn155" class="footnoteRef" id="fnref155"><sup>155</sup></a> I would have emphasized the weapons aspects. But I know you‚Äôre down on bombs.</p>
<p>‚ÄìWell, we‚Äôve got Avalon. That‚Äôs for sure.</p>
