<p>Highet looked at him with loathing. ‚ÄìYou want to change the sensors. The day before the shot.</p>
<p>‚ÄìI want to try hydrogen.</p>
<p>‚ÄìThat‚Äôs an incredibly bad idea, that‚Äôs totally braindead, to introduce a new measurement technique at this stage. You have to calibrate, you have to</p>
